==English==
===Adjective===

# (very vulgar) An intensifier, used in the same contexts as [[fucking]], but more intense
#: ''I have had it with these '''motherfucking''' snakes on this '''motherfucking''' plane!'' - Samuel L. Jackson in ''Snakes on a Plane''.

